reviewText: Awesome message by Prophetess Juanita Bynum to the body of Christ ! This message was done at World Harvest Ministries in Columbus, Ohio under Pastor Rod Parsely.

I received a broken VHS Tape.  I was very disappointed.  I sent an email to who I thought was the seller.  After several days I decided to get a screw driver and open the case to try fixjng it myself.  I got some scotch tape and patched it up.  I viewed the tape and forgot about being disappointed.  To God Be The Glory!
